{"tid":2265090,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"稱士沙踩被告 辯方：賊喊捉賊","createTime":"2020-10-31T06:59:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-31T07:23:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ea5fe3bd1102b9d1cfee64ade5ae7258e7eecbe0","tid":2265090,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T06:59:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201031/QMAOYRLL4JBTDJSRNYH2KCOC6I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201031%2FQMAOYRLL4JBTDJSRNYH2KCOC6I%2F&d=DHxvyfXarR7adKHN0Usak3yU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=fa84f22f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201031%2FQMAOYRLL4JBTDJSRNYH2KCOC6I%2F&h=174ea922\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201031/QMAOYRLL4JBTDJSRNYH2KCOC6I/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n稱士沙踩被告 辯方：賊喊捉賊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/8mRSPzmLZRem46jygjYfssopr8Y=/843x584/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JQMCFM6DMREVTOPQOO45KVUVG4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F8mRSPzmLZRem46jygjYfssopr8Y%3D%2F843x584%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJQMCFM6DMREVTOPQOO45KVUVG4.jpg&h=a9b8ddeb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■被告黃浩峰被指碰撞警署警長張基要（圓圖），昨由聲援者撐傘護送離開。<br />\n<br />\n【襲警案】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】去年聖誕節，。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。，辯方庭上播出港台新聞片段，質疑當日其實是警署警長踩被告在先，二人才有身體接觸，直指警署警長「賊喊捉賊」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n播片證走近被告<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n張昨供稱，當日他身穿防暴裝束執勤，在德福廣場內「高調巡邏」，並截查某些身穿特定衣着、攜帶大型背囊、雨傘或行山杖的人。其後警方收隊，他與同僚前行至案發地點時，全身黑色打扮的被告突然踏前一步，用右半身撞他左邊膊頭，令他身體向橫移動。他斷定被告蓄意碰撞，遂捉住被告並大叫「襲警」，同僚上前拘捕被告。<br />\n<br />\n辯方庭上播放香港電台新聞片段，指張當日取道經過現場時，身邊仍有不少空位，卻偏偏走近被告身旁，並用左腳踩被告右腳。張否認謂：「我冇踢過、冇掂過、冇踩過佢隻腳，冇任何身體接觸。」辯方再指，被告當時沒有踏前一步，反而是張主動踩被告腳面，繼而用左膊撞被告右膊，並喊襲警。張激動指辯方說法屬虛構。<br />\n<br />\n案件表證成立，被告不作供，亦不傳召證人。案件下月4日裁決。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：KTCC1056/20"},{"pid":"db1bfdefb4ff81efc92e80f0489d0bcb174a6682","tid":2265090,"uid":88860,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T07:18:51.000Z","msg":"士沙咩黎嫁？咪又係員佐仔"},{"pid":"a352b01525e253ab3290ec74d24d474d2c0e2e7b","tid":2265090,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T07:21:06.000Z","msg":"狗屎垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79bce21b55f7a0805bc753b139dfe07174fd26a6","tid":2265090,"uid":283700,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"db1bfdefb4ff81efc92e80f0489d0bcb174a6682","tid":2265090,"uid":88860,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T07:18:51.000Z","msg":"士沙咩黎嫁？咪又係員佐仔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T07:23:23.000Z","msg":"警長但無得坐館果隻  高級d既畜生"}]}